<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Futuristic Portfolio CTA</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --iv-primary: #4E70F1;
      --iv-secondary: #FBAB9C;
      --iv-dark: #050816;
      --iv-panel: rgba(12,18,38,0.82);
      --iv-panel-2: rgba(17,24,39,0.72);
      --iv-border: rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      --iv-text-soft: rgba(255,255,255,0.78);
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html, body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: #050816;
      color: #fff;
      font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
    }

    img {
      max-width: 100%;
      display: block;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
    }

    .iv-portfolio-proof {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #050816;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 80px 0;
      isolation: isolate;
    }

    .iv-portfolio-proof__bg {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .iv-portfolio-proof__orb {
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 999px;
      filter: blur(70px);
      opacity: 0.25;
    }

    .iv-portfolio-proof__orb--left {
      top: -80px;
      left: -120px;
      width: 280px;
      height: 280px;
      background: var(--iv-primary);
    }

    .iv-portfolio-proof__orb--right {
      top: 80px;
      right: -90px;
      width: 320px;
      height: 320px;
      background: var(--iv-secondary);
      opacity: 0.18;
    }

    .iv-portfolio-proof__overlay {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(255,255,255,0.08), transparent 32%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(78,112,241,0.10), transparent 35%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #050816 0%, #081022 45%, #050816 100%);
    }

    .iv-portfolio-proof__grid {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      opacity: 0.08;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.55) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.55) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 40px 40px;
    }

    .iv-portfolio-proof__container {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 1260px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 24px;
    }

    .iv-portfolio-proof__hero {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 48px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .iv-portfolio-proof__eyebrow,
    .iv-panel__eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      margin: 0 0 20px;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(78,112,241,0.14), rgba(251,171,156,0.12));
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.82);
    }

    .iv-portfolio-proof__eyebrow-dot {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--iv-secondary);
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .iv-portfolio-proof__heading {
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 700px;
      font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
      line-height: 1.04;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .iv-portfolio-proof__subheading {
      margin: 24px 0 0;
      max-width: 640px;
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.85;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    }

    .iv-portfolio-proof__actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 32px;
    }

    .iv-btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 48px;
      padding: 13px 26px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .iv-btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .iv-btn--primary {
      color: #fff;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--iv-primary), #8aa1ff);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 42px rgba(78,112,241,0.30);
    }

    .iv-btn--secondary {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    }

    .iv-portfolio-proof__mockup-wrap {
      position: relative;
    }

    .iv-portfolio-proof__mockup-glow {
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 999px;
      filter: blur(70px);
      z-index: 0;
      opacity: 0.18;
    }

    .iv-portfolio-proof__mockup-glow--left {
      top: 30px;
      left: -20px;
      width: 180px;
      height: 180px;
      background: var(--iv-primary);
    }

    .iv-portfolio-proof__mockup-glow--right {
      right: -12px;
      bottom: 24px;
      width: 180px;
      height: 180px;
      background: var(--iv-secondary);
      opacity: 0.14;
    }

    .iv-browser {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 28px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
    }

    .iv-browser__frame {
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 22px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      background: #091022;
    }

    .iv-browser__bar {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    }

    .iv-browser__bar span {
      width: 12px;
      height: 12px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .iv-browser__bar span:nth-child(1) { background: #ff8f84; }
    .iv-browser__bar span:nth-child(2) { background: #ffd36b; }
    .iv-browser__bar span:nth-child(3) { background: #6ad38c; }

    .iv-browser__address {
      margin-left: 10px;
      padding: 5px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.20);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    }

    .iv-browser__content {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 0.92fr 1.08fr;
    }

    .iv-browser__content-left {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 460px;
      padding: 32px;
      border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(78,112,241,0.10), rgba(251,171,156,0.08) 65%, transparent);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .iv-browser__radials {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 30% 25%, rgba(78,112,241,0.18), transparent 28%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 65%, rgba(251,171,156,0.16), transparent 26%);
      opacity: 0.75;
    }

    .iv-browser__brand {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      max-width: 320px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .iv-browser__brand-mark {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 160px;
      height: 160px;
      margin: 0 auto 24px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      box-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(78,112,241,0.18);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    }

    .iv-browser__brand-mark svg {
      width: 112px;
      height: 112px;
      object-fit: contain;
      display: block;
    }

    .iv-browser__badge {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.28em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
    }

    .iv-browser__title {
      margin: 14px 0 0;
      font-size: 30px;
      line-height: 1.15;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .iv-browser__text {
      margin: 14px auto 0;
      max-width: 270px;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.9;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
    }

    .iv-browser__content-right {
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .iv-card-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }

    .iv-card {
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }

    .iv-card--featured {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    }

    .iv-card--gradient {
      margin-top: 16px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(78,112,241,0.14), rgba(251,171,156,0.12));
    }

    .iv-card__top {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .iv-card__icon {
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      flex: 0 0 44px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    }

    .iv-card__label {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.40);
    }

    .iv-card__title {
      margin: 10px 0 0;
      font-size: 20px;
      line-height: 1.3;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .iv-card__title--small {
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .iv-card__text {
      margin: 10px 0 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.9;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
    }

    .iv-list {
      margin: 14px 0 0;
      padding: 0;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .iv-list li {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: flex-start;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.85;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    }

    .iv-list li + li {
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    .iv-list span {
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      margin-top: 9px;
      flex: 0 0 10px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--iv-primary);
    }

    .iv-list li:nth-child(2) span {
      background: var(--iv-secondary);
    }

    .iv-browser__microcopy {
      margin-top: 16px;
      padding: 16px 20px;
      border-radius: 22px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.9;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.60);
    }

    .iv-portfolio-proof__lower {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
      gap: 24px;
      margin-top: 56px;
    }

    .iv-panel {
      padding: 28px;
      border-radius: 28px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.28);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    }

    .iv-panel--text {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    }

    .iv-panel--cta {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.06), rgba(255,255,255,0.03));
    }

    .iv-panel__heading {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3vw, 2.4rem);
      line-height: 1.15;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .iv-panel__richtext {
      margin-top: 18px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.70);
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.9;
    }

    .iv-panel__richtext p {
      margin: 0 0 14px;
    }

    .iv-panel__richtext p:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .iv-panel__quote {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 32px;
      line-height: 1.2;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .iv-benefits {
      margin-top: 28px;
    }

    .iv-benefit {
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
    }

    .iv-benefit + .iv-benefit {
      margin-top: 14px;
    }

    .iv-benefit__title {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .iv-benefit__text {
      margin: 6px 0 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
    }

    .iv-portfolio-proof__actions--bottom {
      margin-top: 28px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1100px) {
      .iv-portfolio-proof__hero,
      .iv-portfolio-proof__lower,
      .iv-browser__content {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .iv-browser__content-left {
        min-height: auto;
        border-right: 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 767px) {
      .iv-portfolio-proof {
        padding: 60px 0;
      }

      .iv-portfolio-proof__container {
        padding: 0 18px;
      }

      .iv-portfolio-proof__hero {
        gap: 34px;
      }

      .iv-portfolio-proof__heading {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
      }

      .iv-portfolio-proof__subheading,
      .iv-panel__richtext {
        font-size: 15px;
      }

      .iv-browser__content-left,
      .iv-browser__content-right,
      .iv-panel,
      .iv-card {
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .iv-browser__title {
        font-size: 24px;
      }

      .iv-panel__quote {
        font-size: 26px;
      }

      .iv-card-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .iv-portfolio-proof__actions {
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .iv-btn {
        width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <section class="iv-portfolio-proof">
    <div class="iv-portfolio-proof__bg">
      <div class="iv-portfolio-proof__orb iv-portfolio-proof__orb--left"></div>
      <div class="iv-portfolio-proof__orb iv-portfolio-proof__orb--right"></div>
      <div class="iv-portfolio-proof__overlay"></div>
      <div class="iv-portfolio-proof__grid"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="iv-portfolio-proof__container">
      <div class="iv-portfolio-proof__hero">
        <div class="iv-portfolio-proof__hero-copy">
          <p class="iv-portfolio-proof__eyebrow">
            <span class="iv-portfolio-proof__eyebrow-dot"></span>
            Why a Portfolio Website Works
          </p>

          <h2 class="iv-portfolio-proof__heading">
            Your résumé gets you seen. Your website gets you remembered.
          </h2>

          <p class="iv-portfolio-proof__subheading">
            A portfolio website helps employers move beyond a list of classes and job titles
            by showing real skills, projects, and professional readiness in one polished place.
          </p>

          <div class="iv-portfolio-proof__actions">
            <a href="#start" class="iv-btn iv-btn--primary">Start Your Website</a>
            <a href="#examples" class="iv-btn iv-btn--secondary">Browse Examples</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="iv-portfolio-proof__mockup-wrap">
          <div class="iv-portfolio-proof__mockup-glow iv-portfolio-proof__mockup-glow--left"></div>
          <div class="iv-portfolio-proof__mockup-glow iv-portfolio-proof__mockup-glow--right"></div>

          <div class="iv-browser">
            <div class="iv-browser__frame">
              <div class="iv-browser__bar">
                <span></span><span></span><span></span>
                <div class="iv-browser__address">portfolio.preview</div>
              </div>

              <div class="iv-browser__content">
                <div class="iv-browser__content-left">
                  <div class="iv-browser__radials"></div>

                  <div class="iv-browser__brand">
                    <div class="iv-browser__brand-mark">
                      <svg viewBox="0 0 220 220" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
                        <defs>
                          <linearGradient id="swanGradient" x1="36" y1="32" x2="182" y2="182" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
                            <stop stop-color="#4E70F1"/>
                            <stop offset="1" stop-color="#FBAB9C"/>
                          </linearGradient>
                        </defs>
                        <path d="M145 44c-18 4-29 18-29 35 0 8 3 15 8 21-22 2-42 14-57 34 12-6 24-9 37-9 12 0 24 3 35 10 14 9 31 13 49 11-14 11-31 18-51 18-44 0-76-30-92-63 0 48 39 86 96 86 43 0 75-18 96-47-29 10-58 7-79-8-9-7-20-11-31-12 14-8 23-22 23-38 0-16-2-28-5-38z" fill="url(#swanGradient)"/>
                        <path d="M147 48c10 16 12 34 8 52" stroke="white" stroke-opacity="0.45" stroke-width="7" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                        <path d="M80 125c17-1 33 4 47 13" stroke="white" stroke-opacity="0.38" stroke-width="6" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                      </svg>
                    </div>

                    <p class="iv-browser__badge">Graduate Portfolio</p>
                    <h3 class="iv-browser__title">Built to look sharp. Designed to stand out.</h3>
                    <p class="iv-browser__text">
                      A polished online presence gives employers a faster, clearer view of your
                      skills, projects, and professional potential.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="iv-browser__content-right">
                  <div class="iv-card iv-card--featured">
                    <div class="iv-card__top">
                      <div>
                        <p class="iv-card__label">Featured Project</p>
                        <h4 class="iv-card__title">Predictive Analytics Dashboard</h4>
                        <p class="iv-card__text">
                          Showcase a featured project with visuals, outcomes, tools used,
                          and what you learned.
                        </p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="iv-card__icon"></div>
                    </div>
                  </div>

                  <div class="iv-card-grid">
                    <div class="iv-card">
                      <p class="iv-card__label">Skills</p>
                      <h4 class="iv-card__title iv-card__title--small">Python • SQL • Tableau</h4>
                      <p class="iv-card__text">
                        Highlight technical or professional skills in a format that's easy to scan.
                      </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="iv-card">
                      <p class="iv-card__label">Experience</p>
                      <h4 class="iv-card__title iv-card__title--small">Research • Leadership • Experience</h4>
                      <p class="iv-card__text">
                        Make your internships, coursework, service, and roles feel organized and credible.
                      </p>
                    </div>
                  </div>

                  <div class="iv-card iv-card--gradient">
                    <p class="iv-card__label">Why it works</p>
                    <ul class="iv-list">
                      <li><span></span>Shows real work, not just bullet points.</li>
                      <li><span></span>Helps employers understand strengths faster.</li>
                      <li><span></span>Creates a polished, memorable first impression.</li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="iv-browser__microcopy">
              A portfolio website doesn’t replace your résumé or LinkedIn profile. It strengthens both.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="iv-portfolio-proof__lower">
        <div class="iv-panel iv-panel--text">
          <p class="iv-panel__eyebrow">Research-backed advantage</p>
          <h3 class="iv-panel__heading">Employers don’t just want claims. They want evidence.</h3>
          <div class="iv-panel__richtext">
            <p>
              Recruiter and employer research consistently shows that candidates who can demonstrate
              skills through projects and work samples are easier to evaluate and more likely to stand out.
            </p>
            <p>
              A portfolio website gives hiring managers something a résumé alone cannot:
              a fuller picture of capability, initiative, and potential.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="iv-panel iv-panel--cta">
          <p class="iv-panel__eyebrow">Call to action</p>
          <blockquote class="iv-panel__quote">
            “Don’t just tell employers what you’ve done—show them.”
          </blockquote>

          <div class="iv-benefits">
            <div class="iv-benefit">
              <h4 class="iv-benefit__title">Shows real work</h4>
              <p class="iv-benefit__text">
                Projects, writing, and accomplishments create stronger proof than bullet points alone.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="iv-benefit">
              <h4 class="iv-benefit__title">Feels polished and professional</h4>
              <p class="iv-benefit__text">
                A modern personal site signals initiative, preparation, and confidence.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="iv-benefit">
              <h4 class="iv-benefit__title">Grows with your career</h4>
              <p class="iv-benefit__text">
                Keep updating it as you add experience, goals, and better work over time.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="iv-portfolio-proof__actions iv-portfolio-proof__actions--bottom">
            <a href="#start" class="iv-btn iv-btn--primary">Start Your Website</a>
            <a href="#examples" class="iv-btn iv-btn--secondary">Browse Examples</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</body>
</html>